To forward a version of a package:
1 - Expand the package.
2 - Click on the version you want to forward.
3 - Click the 'Forward' button. If you don't see a 'Forward' button then click 'More actions' and select 'Forward'.
4 - In the dialog that appears, select the names of the people that you want to forward the version to.
5 - You can also type the name of a contact or an e-mail address in the text control. As you type, a menu may appear making suggestions. You can select a name from the list to save you typing the whole name.
6 - Multiple entries should be separated by commas.
7 - Press the 'Forward' button.